{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I finish in in three and a half years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put it this way, and I figured out what the-- I want to go to there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I personally want to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I want to prove that we are not any different, the Jews, than any other Polish Catholic boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they send me to the most strictest, the most difficult officer school to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was [INAUDIBLE] city of Germans because [NON-ENGLISH] was annexed to Germany 'til 1918.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In 1919, they got the part of the Germany to Poland-- originally was always for century Polish ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the [NON-ENGLISH] was lots of German family who became Polish citizen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in this particular officer school-- this was close to about 400 students in the [INAUDIBLE], 90% were the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We called them Wasserpolak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the only one Jew in the officer school, and-- and-- I'll tell you something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were certain requirement for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are the best, or you're out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you are not the best, you going to the army for two years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or you want to finish in one year, you have to be best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- I finished with the highest rank from the officer school, as a sergeant officer candidate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And three of us was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You saw the picture.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two boys who are friends of mine, and this was suddenly the picture, we were the three top in the class.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have right away a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From all over the Poland, the all Jewish private school was looking for a teacher of physical education.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, I have a right to teach ROTC as a officer candidate because I was nominated in 1938 for full-fledged officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the guy what was important.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
